OL,3,CChorley MP says local elections should
OL,4,Cgo ahead, despite council position
OL,6,FBut in an email shared exclusively
OL,7,Fwith ITV News, Hoyle, who is also the
OL,8,FChorley MP, said he "personally
OL,9,Fbelieve(s) that the local elections on
OL,10,FMay 2026 should take place".
OL,12,FHe added he did not "believe in
OL,13,Fcancelling elections" in principle.
OL,15,FThe email was sent on January 12, just
OL,16,Fdays before the deadline for councils
OL,17,Fto write to the government requesting
OL,18,Fa delay.
