OL,6,FIn December 2025, ministers wrote to
OL,7,F63 councils that were scheduled to
OL,8,Fhold elections in May, offering the
OL,9,Foption to push them back because the
OL,10,Frestructure is taking longer than
OL,11,Fexpected.
OL,13,FITV News research has found that 29
OL,14,Fcouncils have written to the council
OL,15,Frequesting to push back their ballots.
OL,16,F20 of these are run by Labour majority
OL,17,For minority organisations.
